This is a simple investment calculator built with React. It allows users to calculate their potential investment returns based on their initial investment amount, annual interest rate, and investment duration.

Features
User-friendly interface for inputting investment details
Real-time calculation of potential investment returns
Displays the final investment value after the specified duration
Responsive design for use on different devices
Installation
To run this application locally, follow these steps:

Clone the repository:


git clone https://github.com/your-username/investment-calculator.git
Navigate to the project directory:


cd investment-calculator
Install the required dependencies:


npm install
Start the development server:


npm run dev
The application should now be running at http://localhost:5174.

Usage
Enter the initial investment amount in the designated input field.
Enter the annual investment rate.
Enter the investment duration in years.
The calculator will automatically update and display the potential investment value after the specified duration.
Technologies Used
React
JavaScript
HTML
CSS


